ocl:
context Hospital
inv: self.name <> null implies self.address <> null

context Hospital
inv: not(self.name <> null and self.address <> null)

context Patient
inv: self.admissions->notEmpty() implies self.admissions->sortedBy(x | x.admitDate)->first().admitDate <= self.admissions->sortedBy(x | x.admitDate)->last().admitDate

context MedicalRecord
inv: self.prescriptions->size() >= 4 implies self.prescriptions->asSequence()->at(4).prescriptionNo <> null

context Patient
inv: self.appointments->notEmpty() implies self.appointments->sortedBy(x | x.dateTime)->first().dateTime <= self.appointments->sortedBy(x | x.dateTime)->last().dateTime

context Admission
inv: self.admitDate <> '' and self.admitDate.size() > 0

context Department
inv: self.name <> '' and self.name.size() > 0

context Invoice
inv: self.totalAmount >= 37 and self.totalAmount <= 85

context Person
inv: self.fullName <> null implies self.phone <> null

context Admission
inv: self.admissionId.size() >= 5 implies self.admissionId.substring(1, 5) = 'value'

context Doctor
inv: self.doctorId <> null implies self.specialty <> null

context Procedure
inv: self.performedAt.size() >= 10 implies self.performedAt.substring(1, 10) = 'value'

context Admission
inv: not(self.admitDate.size() >= 10 implies self.admitDate.substring(1, 10) = 'value')

context Appointment
inv: not(self.appointmentId.size() >= 5 implies self.appointmentId.substring(1, 5) = 'value')

context Admission
inv: not(self.admitDate.size() >= 5 implies self.admitDate.substring(1, 5) = 'value')

context MedicalRecord
inv: (self.diagnoses->notEmpty() implies self.diagnoses->last().diagnosedAt <> null) and (self.diagnoses->isEmpty())

context Prescription
inv: (self.medications->notEmpty() implies self.medications->first().frequency <> null) and (self.medications->isEmpty())

context Department
inv: (self.nurses->notEmpty() implies self.nurses->sortedBy(x | x.shift)->first().shift <= self.nurses->sortedBy(x | x.shift)->last().shift) and (self.nurses->isEmpty())
